{"tid":1771813,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大喜屋集團 再次遞交上市申請","createTime":"2019-12-06T06:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T09:22:48.000Z","uid":12896,"like":20,"dislike":291,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"bccb187a4a6da93ed154d76fd032f0c8ce553de0","tid":1771813,"uid":12896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:31:09.000Z","msg":"在香港經營14間餐廳、專營日式放題料理的大喜屋集團控股遞交再次上市申請。獨家保薦人同人融資。<br />\n<br />\n大喜屋旗下品牌包括大瀛喜、大滿喜、吉壽及岩鹽。截至今年3月底止年度，溢利9,220.8萬元，按年增147.2%，主要由於整體收入因擴張餐廳網絡而增加；及與2018財年相比，2019財年並無產生以股份為基礎的付款開支。<br />\n<br />\n而截至今年7月底止四個月，溢利1,268.2萬元，按年跌66.1%，主要由於香港社會動蕩導致整體收入減少；開業新餐廳導致員工成本及其他經營開支增加等原因所致。<br />\n<br />\n大喜屋曾於今年6月4日遞交招股文件，由於已經超過半年，申請日前失效<br />\n<br />\nCredit to AASTOCK<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.980793/3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.980793%2F3&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=0c403fb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.980793/3</a><br />\n<br />\n手足要做野了，全面裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以比佢上到市<br />\n除左裝修，有冇金融撚知可以點做，可以搞9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0180f32696c7c682389586bec910698252832d9b","tid":1771813,"uid":12609,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"藍"},{"pid":"f9aac68a822acaeea78b87113bfd981ef26246dc","tid":1771813,"uid":248499,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"同br Pacific 一樣，想上市 cap水走人"},{"pid":"58f4f698d3a7beaadb0bc49a03377a9e3a92b465","tid":1771813,"uid":248499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9aac68a822acaeea78b87113bfd981ef26246dc","tid":1771813,"uid":248499,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"同br Pacific 一樣，想上市 cap水走人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:37: